# Kealee Platform v20 — Core Rules

## Stack
- Framework: Next.js (portal apps), Fastify (services/API)
- ORM: Prisma (368 models) on Supabase (PostgreSQL + pgvector)
- Payments: Stripe live mode (43 products)
- Cache: Redis — NEVER silently skip (GAP-03 is critical)
- Queue: core-events pub/sub
- Infra: Railway (services + API) + Vercel (6 portal apps)
- Language: TypeScript strict everywhere — no plain JS in src/

## Absolute Rules (Never Violate)
- NEVER hardcode prices — always import from `packages/core-rules/src/pricing.ts`
- NEVER deploy without SESSION 12 smoke test
- NEVER reference Zem Solutions anywhere in code, comments, or docs
- NEVER run EstimateBot or PermitBot without prior bot output in chain
- NEVER link portal subdomains from web-main CTAs
- NEVER use raw Anthropic SDK — always use ClaudeCachedClient
- NEVER add garden/landscape/kitchen flows that bypass AI Concept first
- NEVER silently catch Redis errors — throw and alert
- NEVER ship without dist/ builds across all packages/services/bots

## Build Order (Strict)
core-rules → core-events → core-bots → core-ddts → core-bim
→ 6 services → 13 bots → API router
